These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, turtle, pony, horse
1. the owner of the turtle is between the owner of the pony and the owner of the horse##2
2. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Pet   | mouse | horse | turtle | pony |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, turkish, thai, italian
1. the italian is on the right of the turkish##1
2. the thai is on the right of the american##1
3. the italian is between the turkish and the american##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Nationality   | turkish | italian | american | thai |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, indie, folk, classical
1. the fan classical is on the right of the fan gospel##1
2. the fan folk is between the fan indie and the fan classical##2
3. the fan gospel is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | classical | folk | indie |

 #################################

 
