.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-15::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, april, october, july
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's birthday is in april##2
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Birthday   | may | april | october | july |

