2. the person who's sport is golf is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who's sport is cricket##2
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |    2     |    3     |  4   |
| Sport   | cricket | golf | snowboarding | weightlifting |

