.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-20::.
House: wooden, cape-cod, palace, townhouse
1. the wooden house is between the palace house and the cape-cod house##2
2. the cape-cod house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
3. the cape-cod house is on the right of the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| House   | palace | wooden | cape-cod | townhouse |

 